1946;;Undercurrent;;American;;Vincente Minnelli;;Katharine Hepburn, Robert Mitchum;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Undercurrent_(1946_film);;Ann Hamilton (Katharine Hepburn) is a middle-aged bride who begins to suspect that her charming husband Alan Garroway (Taylor) plans to murder her. Neither can she ignore her brother-in-law, Michael Garroway (Mitchum), whom she has never met, but has been told so much about.